{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body>\n<div class=\"newsEntryContainer\">\n\n<img alt=\"五一黃金周｜截至早上10時近18.9萬人次出入境　其中逾6萬內地訪客\" class=\"entryImg\" src=\"https://img.tvb.com/inews_admin/pro/20260503/entry_horizontal_69f6da2456e3a93ac7323e24_1777785531562_640x360.jpg\" title=\"五一黃金周｜截至早上10時近18.9萬人次出入境　其中逾6萬內地訪客\"/>\n<h6>\n<blockquote>今日截至早上10時有近18.9萬人次出入境，其中逾6萬內地訪客、4萬港人入境。</blockquote>\n</h6>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-03T05:50:46.865596+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":39,"images":1,"source":"TVB 新聞","fallback":"none"}}